metadata.name: Founding Member
metadata.description: Nvak Collective Founding Members bring together a highly curated group of people that we trust and admire across various creative and business sectors – music, tech, finance, fashion, film, t.v., photography, philanthropy, and more. It is important to us that the artists on our roster have mentors and role models that they can emulate and look up to. Holding this Founding Membership acts as an ALL ACCESS PASS to the Nvak Collective ecosystem -- a dynamic world of immersive music, content, and experiences await ✨
